lead_paragraph: Caroline Coyer scored 18 of her 25 points in the second half, Katherine Coyer made a free throw with 6.2 seconds left and Villanova beat No. 24 DePaul 64-60 on Sunday to knock off the lone unbeaten team in Big East play.

headline.print_headline: Villanova Women Hand No. 24 DePaul 1st Big East Loss, 64-60
